{"update_time":"2019-06-16T16:16:23.310Z","content":{"html":"<div data-block-id=\"ee64ec64-c1b3-48ae-9a91-21ceb3dbf58c\" class=\"notion-selectable\" style=\"width: 100%; max-width: calc((100vw - 0px) - 192px); margin-top: 2px; margin-bottom: 1px;\"><div style=\"color: rgb(55, 53, 47);\"><div style=\"display: flex;\"><div contenteditable=\"false\" spellcheck=\"true\" placeholder=\" \" data-root=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: break-word; caret-color: rgb(55, 53, 47); padding: 3px 2px;\">起因是这样的</div></div></div></div><div data-block-id=\"7ac1e6ca-97b7-4e16-ac26-400414782d1d\" class=\"notion-selectable\" style=\"width: 100%; max-width: calc(100vw - 0px); align-self: center; margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em;\"><div><div style=\"display: flex;\"><div class=\"notion-cursor-default\" style=\"position: relative; overflow: hidden; flex-grow: 1;\"><div style=\"position: relative;\"><div style=\"height: 100%; width: 100%;\"><img src=\"https://www.notion.so/image/https%3A%2F%2Fs3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com%2Fsecure.notion-static.com%2F9a3be4b5-68ae-4dbc-ace0-8759f711c4b4%2F005A42C5-ABE6-4676-92EF-F2B7A1945FEF.jpeg?table=block&amp;id=7ac1e6ca-97b7-4e16-ac26-400414782d1d&amp;width=3340&amp;cache=v2\" style=\"display: block; object-fit: cover; border-radius: 1px; width: 100%; pointer-events: auto;\"></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-block-id=\"9ed54a11-76b0-4070-afdc-a19a34d26c40\" class=\"notion-selectable\" style=\"width: 100%; max-width: calc((100vw - 0px) - 192px); margin-top: 1px; margin-bottom: 1px;\"><div style=\"color: rgb(55, 53, 47);\"><div style=\"display: flex;\"><div contenteditable=\"false\" spellcheck=\"true\" placeholder=\" \" data-root=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: break-word; caret-color: rgb(55, 53, 47); padding: 3px 2px;\">参考红线部分的内容，今天刷即刻的时候，发现了这条评论。遂在 iPad 上尝试了一下 PWA 版即刻，体验不还错。</div></div></div></div><div data-block-id=\"6ed3e837-99d7-4723-9460-dfced0d20e98\" class=\"notion-selectable\" style=\"width: 100%; max-width: calc((100vw - 0px) - 192px); margin-top: 1px; margin-bottom: 1px;\"><div style=\"color: rgb(55, 53, 47);\"><div style=\"display: flex;\"><div contenteditable=\"false\" spellcheck=\"true\" placeholder=\" \" data-root=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: break-word; caret-color: rgb(55, 53, 47); padding: 3px 2px; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(55, 53, 47); -webkit-text-fill-color: rgba(55, 53, 47, 0.4);\"></div></div></div></div><div data-block-id=\"a5c3ed19-2488-4be7-b27a-63ff8099b318\" class=\"notion-selectable\" style=\"width: 100%; max-width: calc((100vw - 0px) - 192px); margin-top: 1px; margin-bottom: 1px;\"><div style=\"color: rgb(55, 53, 47);\"><div style=\"display: flex;\"><div contenteditable=\"false\" spellcheck=\"true\" placeholder=\" \" data-root=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: break-word; caret-color: rgb(55, 53, 47); padding: 3px 2px;\">整体界面比较简洁。最让我瞩目是右下角\"回到顶部\"的按钮，因为在干净的页面上出现一个不和谐的元素。于是我开始思考这个按钮的使用场景，以及它存在的意义。</div></div></div></div><div data-block-id=\"0204b6dd-7da8-4fdf-a653-58f075268187\" class=\"notion-selectable\" style=\"width: 100%; max-width: calc((100vw - 0px) - 192px); margin-top: 1px; margin-bottom: 1px;\"><div style=\"color: rgb(55, 53, 47);\"><div style=\"display: flex;\"><div contenteditable=\"false\" spellcheck=\"true\" placeholder=\" \" data-root=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: break-word; caret-color: rgb(55, 53, 47); padding: 3px 2px; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(55, 53, 47); -webkit-text-fill-color: rgba(55, 53, 47, 0.4);\"></div></div></div></div><div data-block-id=\"62a92693-a693-45ea-a716-1f7c86ade2ae\" class=\"notion-selectable\" style=\"width: 100%; max-width: calc((100vw - 0px) - 192px); margin-top: 1px; margin-bottom: 1px;\"><div style=\"color: rgb(55, 53, 47);\"><div style=\"display: flex;\"><div contenteditable=\"false\" spellcheck=\"true\" placeholder=\" \" data-root=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: break-word; caret-color: rgb(55, 53, 47); padding: 3px 2px;\">功能显而易见，用户在下拉（刷）了很久后，点击这个按钮可以回到页面顶部。可是回到顶部又是为了干什么？我个人理解是，最初这个回到顶部的功能，是为了让用户快速寻找导航栏，进行其它的跳转操作。</div></div></div></div><div data-block-id=\"4e611297-d8f6-430b-98f7-20d7809ced14\" class=\"notion-selectable\" style=\"width: 100%; max-width: calc((100vw - 0px) - 192px); margin-top: 1px; margin-bottom: 1px;\"><div style=\"color: rgb(55, 53, 47);\"><div style=\"display: flex;\"><div contenteditable=\"false\" spellcheck=\"true\" placeholder=\" \" data-root=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: break-word; caret-color: rgb(55, 53, 47); padding: 3px 2px; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(55, 53, 47); -webkit-text-fill-color: rgba(55, 53, 47, 0.4);\"></div></div></div></div><div data-block-id=\"b2d8f3d6-0d2a-4c08-a2d9-b97b3257a0e0\" class=\"notion-selectable\" style=\"width: 100%; max-width: calc((100vw - 0px) - 192px); margin-top: 1px; margin-bottom: 1px;\"><div style=\"color: rgb(55, 53, 47);\"><div style=\"display: flex;\"><div contenteditable=\"false\" spellcheck=\"true\" placeholder=\" \" data-root=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: break-word; caret-color: rgb(55, 53, 47); padding: 3px 2px;\">可以是现在有一部分网页的导航栏，已经是悬挂了，始终定在页面顶部，jike 就是这样的。无论你刷多久，导航栏一直都在那里。</div></div></div></div><div data-block-id=\"31c2b5eb-0ac5-4248-be42-dc3713218982\" class=\"notion-selectable\" style=\"width: 100%; max-width: calc(100vw - 0px); align-self: center; margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em;\"><div><div style=\"display: flex;\"><div class=\"notion-cursor-default\" style=\"position: relative; overflow: hidden; flex-grow: 1;\"><div style=\"position: relative;\"><div style=\"height: 100%; width: 100%;\"><img src=\"https://www.notion.so/image/https%3A%2F%2Fs3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com%2Fsecure.notion-static.com%2Ff5f7f723-92f2-4163-970f-3cc7cd206057%2FUntitled.png?table=block&amp;id=31c2b5eb-0ac5-4248-be42-dc3713218982&amp;width=4060&amp;cache=v2\" style=\"display: block; object-fit: cover; border-radius: 1px; width: 100%; pointer-events: auto;\"></div></div></div></div><div contenteditable=\"false\" spellcheck=\"true\" placeholder=\"Write a caption...\" data-root=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: break-word; caret-color: rgb(55, 53, 47); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4; color: rgba(55, 53, 47, 0.6); padding-top: 6px; padding-bottom: 6px; padding-left: 2px;\">右下角的按钮是否显得突兀？</div></div></div><div data-block-id=\"ea78c662-5bad-433d-a048-0af0699d5800\" class=\"notion-selectable\" style=\"width: 100%; max-width: calc((100vw - 0px) - 192px); margin-top: 1px; margin-bottom: 1px;\"><div style=\"color: rgb(55, 53, 47);\"><div style=\"display: flex;\"><div contenteditable=\"false\" spellcheck=\"true\" placeholder=\" \" data-root=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: break-word; caret-color: rgb(55, 53, 47); padding: 3px 2px; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(55, 53, 47); -webkit-text-fill-color: rgba(55, 53, 47, 0.4);\"></div></div></div></div><div data-block-id=\"6a020dbb-819a-47f1-a217-cd9a0af1382b\" class=\"notion-selectable\" style=\"width: 100%; max-width: calc((100vw - 0px) - 192px); margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 1px; color: rgb(55, 53, 47);\"><div style=\"display: flex; width: 100%; font-weight: 600; font-size: 1.25em; letter-spacing: -0.002em; line-height: 1.2; color: rgb(55, 53, 47);\"><div contenteditable=\"false\" spellcheck=\"true\" placeholder=\"Heading 3\" data-root=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: break-word; caret-color: rgb(55, 53, 47); padding: 3px 2px;\">按钮是否有必要</div></div></div><div data-block-id=\"18dec978-2ce0-43d0-9dac-8fb9f0734658\" class=\"notion-selectable\" style=\"width: 100%; max-width: calc((100vw - 0px) - 192px); margin-top: 1px; margin-bottom: 1px;\"><div style=\"color: rgb(55, 53, 47);\"><div style=\"display: flex;\"><div contenteditable=\"false\" spellcheck=\"true\" placeholder=\" \" data-root=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: break-word; caret-color: rgb(55, 53, 47); padding: 3px 2px;\">所以我们真的需要这个按钮嘛？80%+的键盘 自带的 home 键不好用嘛？如果是移动设备访问，没有键盘。用户想返回顶部，这个按钮确实还是很好用的。</div></div></div></div><div data-block-id=\"d8f6b6cd-72b3-4f27-a881-9ea1407a429d\" class=\"notion-selectable\" style=\"width: 100%; max-width: calc((100vw - 0px) - 192px); margin-top: 1px; margin-bottom: 1px;\"><div style=\"color: rgb(55, 53, 47);\"><div style=\"display: flex;\"><div contenteditable=\"false\" spellcheck=\"true\" placeholder=\" \" data-root=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: break-word; caret-color: rgb(55, 53, 47); padding: 3px 2px; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(55, 53, 47); -webkit-text-fill-color: rgba(55, 53, 47, 0.4);\"></div></div></div></div><div data-block-id=\"e4e925fe-3cec-46c1-aa76-41d8e29861cb\" class=\"notion-selectable\" style=\"width: 100%; max-width: calc((100vw - 0px) - 192px); margin-top: 1px; margin-bottom: 1px;\"><div style=\"color: rgb(55, 53, 47);\"><div style=\"display: flex;\"><div contenteditable=\"false\" spellcheck=\"true\" placeholder=\" \" data-root=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: break-word; caret-color: rgb(55, 53, 47); padding: 3px 2px;\">确实是这样，移动用户没有键盘，返回顶部也确实是刚需。不管是找导航栏，还是想从最开始重新浏览（文章），回到顶部这个功能确实是有必要的。那么怎么才能把这个体验做好呢？</div></div></div></div><div data-block-id=\"0f482891-c3cc-4fa7-afc6-263d3a58be21\" class=\"notion-selectable\" style=\"width: 100%; max-width: calc((100vw - 0px) - 192px); margin-top: 1px; margin-bottom: 1px;\"><div style=\"color: rgb(55, 53, 47);\"><div style=\"display: flex;\"><div contenteditable=\"false\" spellcheck=\"true\" placeholder=\" \" data-root=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: break-word; caret-color: rgb(55, 53, 47); padding: 3px 2px; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(55, 53, 47); -webkit-text-fill-color: rgba(55, 53, 47, 0.4);\"></div></div></div></div><div data-block-id=\"4976ba5d-c109-4efd-93cb-66bb7e65fb59\" class=\"notion-selectable\" style=\"width: 100%; max-width: calc((100vw - 0px) - 192px); margin-top: 1px; margin-bottom: 1px;\"><div style=\"color: rgb(55, 53, 47);\"><div style=\"display: flex;\"><div contenteditable=\"false\" spellcheck=\"true\" placeholder=\" \" data-root=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: break-word; caret-color: rgb(55, 53, 47); padding: 3px 2px;\">在移动设备寸土寸金的小屏幕上，怎么设计得简约不突兀，同时实现这个功能。这是一个值得思考的问题。</div></div></div></div><div data-block-id=\"b9bfd389-9d52-48f8-ad64-b055a38a08a8\" class=\"notion-selectable\" style=\"width: 100%; max-width: calc((100vw - 0px) - 192px); margin-top: 1px; margin-bottom: 1px;\"><div style=\"color: rgb(55, 53, 47);\"><div style=\"display: flex;\"><div contenteditable=\"false\" spellcheck=\"true\" placeholder=\" \" data-root=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: break-word; caret-color: rgb(55, 53, 47); padding: 3px 2px; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(55, 53, 47); -webkit-text-fill-color: rgba(55, 53, 47, 0.4);\"></div></div></div></div><div data-block-id=\"73338665-551a-4074-8488-cdc7ac98d68d\" class=\"notion-selectable\" style=\"width: 100%; max-width: calc((100vw - 0px) - 192px); margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 1px; color: rgb(55, 53, 47);\"><div style=\"display: flex; width: 100%; font-weight: 600; font-size: 1.25em; letter-spacing: -0.002em; line-height: 1.2; color: rgb(55, 53, 47);\"><div contenteditable=\"false\" spellcheck=\"true\" placeholder=\"Heading 3\" data-root=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: break-word; caret-color: rgb(55, 53, 47); padding: 3px 2px;\">如何设计才好</div></div></div><div data-block-id=\"c783397a-557e-4bfd-81fc-853d89e534cd\" class=\"notion-selectable\" style=\"width: 100%; max-width: calc((100vw - 0px) - 192px); margin-top: 1px; margin-bottom: 1px;\"><div style=\"color: rgb(55, 53, 47);\"><div style=\"display: flex;\"><div contenteditable=\"false\" spellcheck=\"true\" placeholder=\" \" data-root=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: break-word; caret-color: rgb(55, 53, 47); padding: 3px 2px;\">先看微博。好吧，微博根本没有这个设计（好在我也不用微博，用户体验管我屁事）</div></div></div></div><div data-block-id=\"0c600f10-6f84-4f41-869c-c4b94c72711b\" class=\"notion-selectable\" style=\"width: 100%; max-width: calc((100vw - 0px) - 192px); margin-top: 1px; margin-bottom: 1px;\"><div style=\"color: rgb(55, 53, 47);\"><div style=\"display: flex;\"><div contenteditable=\"false\" spellcheck=\"true\" placeholder=\" \" data-root=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: break-word; caret-color: rgb(55, 53, 47); padding: 3px 2px; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(55, 53, 47); -webkit-text-fill-color: rgba(55, 53, 47, 0.4);\"></div></div></div></div><div data-block-id=\"422c0bc1-3744-400e-b53e-8f309487b25d\" class=\"notion-selectable\" style=\"width: 100%; max-width: calc((100vw - 0px) - 192px); margin-top: 1px; margin-bottom: 1px;\"><div style=\"color: rgb(55, 53, 47);\"><div style=\"display: flex;\"><div contenteditable=\"false\" spellcheck=\"true\" placeholder=\" \" data-root=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: break-word; caret-color: rgb(55, 53, 47); padding: 3px 2px;\">看看 twitter，等等 twitter 的返回到顶部在哪里？也没有嘛？其实是有的，我也是最近才知道的，这个设计很隐晦。<span style=\"font-weight:600\" data-token-index=\"1\">触摸顶部的导航栏，即可返回顶部</span>。</div></div></div></div><div data-block-id=\"a573b8b8-4aae-458c-82d2-69afc05d0c5e\" class=\"notion-selectable\" style=\"width: 100%; max-width: calc((100vw - 0px) - 192px); margin-top: 1px; margin-bottom: 1px;\"><div style=\"color: rgb(55, 53, 47);\"><div style=\"display: flex;\"><div contenteditable=\"false\" spellcheck=\"true\" placeholder=\" \" data-root=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: break-word; caret-color: rgb(55, 53, 47); padding: 3px 2px; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(55, 53, 47); -webkit-text-fill-color: rgba(55, 53, 47, 0.4);\"></div></div></div></div><div data-block-id=\"8cde43bc-1e58-4586-8e10-59cecf27f86a\" class=\"notion-selectable\" style=\"width: 100%; max-width: calc((100vw - 0px) - 192px); margin-top: 1px; margin-bottom: 1px;\"><div style=\"color: rgb(55, 53, 47);\"><div style=\"display: flex;\"><div contenteditable=\"false\" spellcheck=\"true\" placeholder=\" \" data-root=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: break-word; caret-color: rgb(55, 53, 47); padding: 3px 2px;\">同样的设计在微信朋友圈中也可以体验到，需要<span style=\"font-weight:600\" data-token-index=\"1\">双击</span>导航才能回到顶部。</div></div></div></div><div data-block-id=\"3cce552c-d37c-4f73-a112-20ca597a91ff\" class=\"notion-selectable\" style=\"width: 100%; max-width: calc((100vw - 0px) - 192px); margin-top: 1px; margin-bottom: 1px;\"><div style=\"color: rgb(55, 53, 47);\"><div style=\"display: flex;\"><div contenteditable=\"false\" spellcheck=\"true\" placeholder=\" \" data-root=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: break-word; caret-color: rgb(55, 53, 47); padding: 3px 2px; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(55, 53, 47); -webkit-text-fill-color: rgba(55, 53, 47, 0.4);\"></div></div></div></div><div data-block-id=\"d0043eba-b060-4b23-b446-8993e603e6cf\" class=\"notion-selectable\" style=\"width: 100%; max-width: calc((100vw - 0px) - 192px); margin-top: 1px; margin-bottom: 1px;\"><div style=\"color: rgb(55, 53, 47);\"><div style=\"display: flex;\"><div contenteditable=\"false\" spellcheck=\"true\" placeholder=\" \" data-root=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: break-word; caret-color: rgb(55, 53, 47); padding: 3px 2px;\">如有你是 iOS 用户的话，触摸顶部状态栏即可返回顶部，这是系统层面的支持。（此处应有掌声👏）</div></div></div></div><div data-block-id=\"829f1856-ceba-4115-85ad-079d2409d8c6\" class=\"notion-selectable\" style=\"width: 100%; max-width: calc((100vw - 0px) - 192px); margin-top: 1px; margin-bottom: 1px;\"><div style=\"color: rgb(55, 53, 47);\"><div style=\"display: flex;\"><div contenteditable=\"false\" spellcheck=\"true\" placeholder=\" \" data-root=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: break-word; caret-color: rgb(55, 53, 47); padding: 3px 2px; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(55, 53, 47); -webkit-text-fill-color: rgba(55, 53, 47, 0.4);\"></div></div></div></div><div data-block-id=\"1af95b90-0e70-42e3-b7cf-c227bb916e1b\" class=\"notion-selectable\" style=\"width: 100%; max-width: calc((100vw - 0px) - 192px); margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 1px; color: rgb(55, 53, 47);\"><div style=\"display: flex; width: 100%; font-weight: 600; font-size: 1.25em; letter-spacing: -0.002em; line-height: 1.2; color: rgb(55, 53, 47);\"><div contenteditable=\"false\" spellcheck=\"true\" placeholder=\"Heading 3\" data-root=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: break-word; caret-color: rgb(55, 53, 47); padding: 3px 2px;\">美中不足？</div></div></div><div data-block-id=\"deffa49d-fcfa-4079-ac53-44897e1ecfd2\" class=\"notion-selectable\" style=\"width: 100%; max-width: calc((100vw - 0px) - 192px); margin-top: 1px; margin-bottom: 1px;\"><div style=\"color: rgb(55, 53, 47);\"><div style=\"display: flex;\"><div contenteditable=\"false\" spellcheck=\"true\" placeholder=\" \" data-root=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: break-word; caret-color: rgb(55, 53, 47); padding: 3px 2px;\">看吧总是有解决办法的，既没有突兀的按钮又实现了功能。但是怎么说呢，通过触摸导航栏实现回到顶部这个功能。从设计上来说是不错的，当然易用性也不错。只是有那么一点隐晦，用户很难发现这个功能。</div></div></div></div><div data-block-id=\"0cafdeb0-cb50-4e5e-a8c6-3002b3f9fd13\" class=\"notion-selectable\" style=\"width: 100%; max-width: calc((100vw - 0px) - 192px); margin-top: 1px; margin-bottom: 1px;\"><div style=\"color: rgb(55, 53, 47);\"><div style=\"display: flex;\"><div contenteditable=\"false\" spellcheck=\"true\" placeholder=\" \" data-root=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: break-word; caret-color: rgb(55, 53, 47); padding: 3px 2px; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(55, 53, 47); -webkit-text-fill-color: rgba(55, 53, 47, 0.4);\"></div></div></div></div><div data-block-id=\"35964fdd-e367-42c6-b9fb-e99952417fb4\" class=\"notion-selectable\" style=\"width: 100%; max-width: calc((100vw - 0px) - 192px); margin-top: 1px; margin-bottom: 1px;\"><div style=\"color: rgb(55, 53, 47);\"><div style=\"display: flex;\"><div contenteditable=\"false\" spellcheck=\"true\" placeholder=\" \" data-root=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: break-word; caret-color: rgb(55, 53, 47); padding: 3px 2px;\">或许有的读者也是在看着这篇文章时，才知道这些功能的。看起来似乎完美，但是用户却不懂这个设计。这可能是最让设计师头疼的事情。</div></div></div></div><div data-block-id=\"650e1cb7-51bd-4ba1-a8ce-3fc2a537a4cc\" class=\"notion-selectable\" style=\"width: 100%; max-width: calc((100vw - 0px) - 192px); margin-top: 1px; margin-bottom: 1px;\"><div style=\"color: rgb(55, 53, 47);\"><div style=\"display: flex;\"><div contenteditable=\"false\" spellcheck=\"true\" placeholder=\" \" data-root=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: break-word; caret-color: rgb(55, 53, 47); padding: 3px 2px; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(55, 53, 47); -webkit-text-fill-color: rgba(55, 53, 47, 0.4);\"></div></div></div></div><div data-block-id=\"fa8deb7a-73ac-4efe-8d21-d6b2b30ebf99\" class=\"notion-selectable\" style=\"width: 100%; max-width: calc((100vw - 0px) - 192px); margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 1px; color: rgb(55, 53, 47);\"><div style=\"display: flex; width: 100%; font-weight: 600; font-size: 1.25em; letter-spacing: -0.002em; line-height: 1.2; color: rgb(55, 53, 47);\"><div contenteditable=\"false\" spellcheck=\"true\" placeholder=\"Heading 3\" data-root=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: break-word; caret-color: rgb(55, 53, 47); padding: 3px 2px;\">杂谈</div></div></div><div data-block-id=\"746ae734-ac3d-4702-8df4-a918d05f5699\" class=\"notion-selectable\" style=\"width: 100%; max-width: calc((100vw - 0px) - 192px); margin-top: 1px; margin-bottom: 1px;\"><div style=\"color: rgb(55, 53, 47);\"><div style=\"display: flex;\"><div contenteditable=\"false\" spellcheck=\"true\" placeholder=\" \" data-root=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: break-word; caret-color: rgb(55, 53, 47); padding: 3px 2px;\">不管是网页、 App 、还是游戏。所有有用户交互的地方，那些堪称艺术、令人赏心悦目的作品。它们的界面都是简约的。Procreate、纪念碑谷、notion 等等莫不如此。</div></div></div></div><div data-block-id=\"8d02369a-8ac3-4ae5-958c-8366d465aa28\" class=\"notion-selectable\" style=\"width: 100%; max-width: calc((100vw - 0px) - 192px); margin-top: 1px; margin-bottom: 1px;\"><div style=\"color: rgb(55, 53, 47);\"><div style=\"display: flex;\"><div contenteditable=\"false\" spellcheck=\"true\" placeholder=\" \" data-root=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: break-word; caret-color: rgb(55, 53, 47); padding: 3px 2px; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(55, 53, 47); -webkit-text-fill-color: rgba(55, 53, 47, 0.4);\"></div></div></div></div><div data-block-id=\"e75fba01-38a9-4c5b-9e98-19fab5fffef1\" class=\"notion-selectable\" style=\"width: 100%; max-width: calc((100vw - 0px) - 192px); margin-top: 1px; margin-bottom: 1px;\"><div style=\"color: rgb(55, 53, 47);\"><div style=\"display: flex;\"><div contenteditable=\"false\" spellcheck=\"true\" placeholder=\" \" data-root=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: break-word; caret-color: rgb(55, 53, 47); padding: 3px 2px;\">notion 的招聘写的很有意思，我们需要会写代码的设计师而不是会设计的程序员。主次关系很明显，设计为重。二者得兼当然是最吼滴。</div></div></div></div><div data-block-id=\"f8e7c274-89cc-47f6-9e9e-d654cbefd48f\" class=\"notion-selectable\" style=\"width: 100%; max-width: calc(100vw - 0px); align-self: center; margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em;\"><div><div style=\"display: flex;\"><div class=\"notion-cursor-default\" style=\"position: relative; overflow: hidden; flex-grow: 1;\"><div style=\"position: relative;\"><div style=\"height: 100%; width: 100%;\"><img src=\"https://www.notion.so/image/https%3A%2F%2Fs3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com%2Fsecure.notion-static.com%2F1eed892f-7ec6-4a31-821c-faac7823b508%2FUntitled.png?table=block&amp;id=f8e7c274-89cc-47f6-9e9e-d654cbefd48f&amp;width=1530&amp;cache=v2\" style=\"display: block; object-fit: cover; border-radius: 1px; width: 100%; pointer-events: auto;\"></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-block-id=\"6c854b50-6890-4106-b220-55860942bd0c\" class=\"notion-selectable\" style=\"width: 100%; max-width: calc((100vw - 0px) - 192px); margin-top: 1px; margin-bottom: 1px;\"><div style=\"color: rgb(55, 53, 47);\"><div style=\"display: flex;\"><div contenteditable=\"false\" spellcheck=\"true\" placeholder=\" \" data-root=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: break-word; caret-color: rgb(55, 53, 47); padding: 3px 2px; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(55, 53, 47); -webkit-text-fill-color: rgba(55, 53, 47, 0.4);\"></div></div></div></div><div data-block-id=\"5bce932a-472c-448f-bb52-653ee76ca7a2\" class=\"notion-selectable\" style=\"width: 100%; max-width: calc((100vw - 0px) - 192px); margin-top: 1px; margin-bottom: 1px;\"><div style=\"color: rgb(55, 53, 47);\"><div style=\"display: flex;\"><div contenteditable=\"false\" spellcheck=\"true\" placeholder=\" \" data-root=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: break-word; caret-color: rgb(55, 53, 47); padding: 3px 2px;\">discord 曾经的招聘信息也很有意思，不过现在我找不到了。简单说来，那时候 discord 刚刚用户爆发增长，他们的的招聘信息全是招设计师。一个把用户体验放在第一位的公司不会太差。</div></div></div></div><div data-block-id=\"504dca5e-db99-408a-901a-d3049ae70f8f\" class=\"notion-selectable\" style=\"width: 100%; max-width: calc((100vw - 0px) - 192px); margin-top: 1px; margin-bottom: 1px;\"><div style=\"color: rgb(55, 53, 47);\"><div style=\"display: flex;\"><div contenteditable=\"false\" spellcheck=\"true\" placeholder=\" \" data-root=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: break-word; caret-color: rgb(55, 53, 47); padding: 3px 2px; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(55, 53, 47); -webkit-text-fill-color: rgba(55, 53, 47, 0.4);\"></div></div></div></div><div data-block-id=\"723c7ede-3689-4f99-9805-0626670139ab\" class=\"notion-selectable\" style=\"width: 100%; max-width: calc((100vw - 0px) - 192px); margin-top: 1px; margin-bottom: 1px;\"><div style=\"color: rgb(55, 53, 47);\"><div style=\"display: flex;\"><div contenteditable=\"false\" spellcheck=\"true\" placeholder=\" \" data-root=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: break-word; caret-color: rgb(55, 53, 47); padding: 3px 2px;\">对于那些设计简约的产品，你可能不知道如何操作。但是没关系，你可以通过探索或者产品引导逐步地去了解它们，这个过程也是非常有趣的。如果你真的没法发现某个功能，这可能是设计师的失败，也可能你不是这个设计的目标用户。</div></div></div></div><div data-block-id=\"a1ca0a5f-d676-49b8-9b79-5b9d2f316408\" class=\"notion-selectable\" style=\"width: 100%; max-width: calc((100vw - 0px) - 192px); margin-top: 1px; margin-bottom: 1px;\"><div style=\"color: rgb(55, 53, 47);\"><div style=\"display: flex;\"><div contenteditable=\"false\" spellcheck=\"true\" placeholder=\" \" data-root=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: break-word; caret-color: rgb(55, 53, 47); padding: 3px 2px; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(55, 53, 47); -webkit-text-fill-color: rgba(55, 53, 47, 0.4);\"></div></div></div></div><div data-block-id=\"fc88f637-4c67-4da7-8397-077cba1773ca\" class=\"notion-selectable\" style=\"width: 100%; max-width: calc((100vw - 0px) - 192px); margin-top: 1px; margin-bottom: 1px;\"><div style=\"color: rgb(55, 53, 47);\"><div style=\"display: flex;\"><div contenteditable=\"false\" spellcheck=\"true\" placeholder=\" \" data-root=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: break-word; caret-color: rgb(55, 53, 47); padding: 3px 2px;\">太多的信息等于没有信息，同样地太多的入口等于没有入口（这似乎是一个万金油式的句子）。国产app 令人眼花缭乱的主页入口是KPI的产物（没错，支付宝！说的就是你）。</div></div></div></div><div data-block-id=\"9f4974e8-9347-4354-b387-a6abb20267ba\" class=\"notion-selectable\" style=\"width: 100%; max-width: calc((100vw - 0px) - 192px); margin-top: 1px; margin-bottom: 1px;\"><div style=\"color: rgb(55, 53, 47);\"><div style=\"display: flex;\"><div contenteditable=\"false\" spellcheck=\"true\" placeholder=\" \" data-root=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: break-word; caret-color: rgb(55, 53, 47); padding: 3px 2px; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(55, 53, 47); -webkit-text-fill-color: rgba(55, 53, 47, 0.4);\"></div></div></div></div><div data-block-id=\"aaedc4b4-daa4-4852-a2df-e47c4a5bf874\" class=\"notion-selectable\" style=\"width: 100%; max-width: calc((100vw - 0px) - 192px); margin-top: 1px; margin-bottom: 1px;\"><div style=\"color: rgb(55, 53, 47);\"><div style=\"display: flex;\"><div contenteditable=\"false\" spellcheck=\"true\" placeholder=\" \" data-root=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: break-word; caret-color: rgb(55, 53, 47); padding: 3px 2px;\">不知道用户体验为何物的产品，或许可以通过它的市场垄断力统治着用户，但是却永远无法赢得用户的尊重。只有那些真正为用户着想的产品，那些设计优秀的产品才能让用户心甘情愿的买单。那才是真正的双赢，这或许就是境界吧。</div></div></div></div><div data-block-id=\"5388da33-1d65-4ec1-b6f0-dbe629f202f3\" class=\"notion-selectable\" style=\"width: 100%; max-width: calc((100vw - 0px) - 192px); margin-top: 1px; margin-bottom: 1px;\"><div style=\"color: rgb(55, 53, 47);\"><div style=\"display: flex;\"><div contenteditable=\"false\" spellcheck=\"true\" placeholder=\" \" data-root=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: break-word; caret-color: rgb(55, 53, 47); padding: 3px 2px; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(55, 53, 47); -webkit-text-fill-color: rgba(55, 53, 47, 0.4);\"></div></div></div></div><div data-block-id=\"64b80be7-91f8-408d-a8dd-3a8d0c2dbffa\" class=\"notion-selectable\" style=\"width: 100%; max-width: calc((100vw - 0px) - 192px); margin-top: 1px; margin-bottom: 1px;\"><div style=\"color: rgb(55, 53, 47);\"><div style=\"display: flex;\"><div contenteditable=\"false\" spellcheck=\"true\" placeholder=\" \" data-root=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: break-word; caret-color: rgb(55, 53, 47); padding: 3px 2px;\">任重而道远，共勉。</div></div></div></div><div data-block-id=\"692a2d09-5865-4789-a8db-aec8fd59d092\" class=\"notion-selectable\" style=\"width: 100%; max-width: calc((100vw - 0px) - 192px); margin-top: 1px; margin-bottom: 1px;\"><div style=\"color: rgb(55, 53, 47);\"><div style=\"display: flex;\"><div contenteditable=\"false\" spellcheck=\"true\" placeholder=\" \" data-root=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: break-word; caret-color: rgb(55, 53, 47); padding: 3px 2px; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(55, 53, 47); -webkit-text-fill-color: rgba(55, 53, 47, 0.4);\"></div></div></div></div><div data-block-id=\"6035031c-2155-4e65-95c4-b3f78f9ad61c\" class=\"notion-selectable\" style=\"width: 100%; max-width: calc((100vw - 0px) - 192px); margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 1px; color: rgb(55, 53, 47);\"><div style=\"display: flex; width: 100%; font-weight: 600; font-size: 1.25em; letter-spacing: -0.002em; line-height: 1.2; color: rgb(55, 53, 47);\"><div contenteditable=\"false\" spellcheck=\"true\" placeholder=\"Heading 3\" data-root=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: break-word; caret-color: rgb(55, 53, 47); padding: 3px 2px;\">回到 Web 上来</div></div></div><div data-block-id=\"e58019b0-2563-438e-bbfd-282943b17b56\" class=\"notion-selectable\" style=\"width: 100%; max-width: calc((100vw - 0px) - 192px); margin-top: 1px; margin-bottom: 1px;\"><div style=\"color: rgb(55, 53, 47);\"><div style=\"display: flex;\"><div contenteditable=\"false\" spellcheck=\"true\" placeholder=\" \" data-root=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: break-word; caret-color: rgb(55, 53, 47); padding: 3px 2px;\">最后，我的建议。</div></div></div></div><div data-block-id=\"3ec7e930-c1c9-4f3d-a72d-308b47d2c6d4\" class=\"notion-selectable\" style=\"width: 100%; max-width: calc((100vw - 0px) - 192px); margin-top: 4px; margin-bottom: 4px;\"><div style=\"font-size: 1.2em; padding: 3px 2px; color: rgb(55, 53, 47); display: flex;\"><div contenteditable=\"false\" spellcheck=\"true\" placeholder=\"Empty Quote\" data-root=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: break-word; caret-color: rgb(55, 53, 47); border-left: 3px solid currentcolor; padding-left: 0.9em; padding-right: 0.9em;\">如果你的顶部导航栏是 fixed 的，那么你可以利用它来做回到顶部的入口。而不需要一个单独 fixed 在某个地方的按钮来做这件事情。</div></div></div><div data-block-id=\"311fa1ba-c4fa-4552-8d4d-5469e2427bc3\" class=\"notion-selectable\" style=\"width: 100%; max-width: calc((100vw - 0px) - 192px); margin-top: 1px; margin-bottom: 0px;\"><div style=\"color: rgb(55, 53, 47);\"><div style=\"display: flex;\"><div contenteditable=\"false\" spellcheck=\"true\" placeholder=\" \" data-root=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: break-word; caret-color: rgb(55, 53, 47); padding: 3px 2px;\">我依照这个建议，将博客的导航设计改了一下，也加上回到顶部的功能。毕竟我喜欢这种性冷淡的设计风格，好看是第一生产力。</div></div></div></div>","brief":"起因是这样的\n参考红线部分的内容，今天刷即刻的时候，发现了这条评论。遂在 iPad 上尝试了一下 PWA 版即刻，体验不还错。\n整体界面比较简洁。最让我瞩目是右下角\"回到顶部\"的按钮，因为在干净的页面"}}